%EDITMAC  --------------------- BIG  MACRO ---------------------------
%COMMAND ===>_ZCMD
+
+THE%BIG+MACRO IS USED TO CREATE BLOCK CHARACTERS IN TEXT.
+
+USE:
+TYPE%BIG+ON THE COMMAND LINE FOLLOWED BY A CHARACTER (A-Z 0-9) THEN PLA
+THE CURSOR IN THE TEXT WHERE YOU WANT THE BLOCK CHARACTER PRESS ENTER.
+
%COMMAND ===> BIG A
+***************************** TOP OF DATA *****************************
+000001  DATA LINE 1 % -+ <== CURSOR
+
+RESULT:
+
+000001  DATA LINE 1     AAAAAAAAAA
+000002  DATA LINE 2    AAAAAAAAAAAA
+000003  DATA LINE 3    AA        AA
+000004  DATA LINE 4    AA        AA
+000005  DATA LINE 5    AA        AA
+000006  DATA LINE 6    AAAAAAAAAAAA
+000007  DATA LINE 7    AAAAAAAAAAAA
+000008  DATA LINE 8    AA        AA
+000009  DATA LINE 9    AA        AA
)PROC
&KEY = .PFKEY
)END
